    Wait, why are you screaming?

06:21.382 --> 06:23.482
I thought that was what
we were doing.

06:23.484 --> 06:25.217
                Well, let's not.
Okeydokey.

06:29.690 --> 06:32.190
            LOUISE:
 So I'm gonna go out on a limb

06:32.192 --> 06:35.360
    and say I may be having
         a fever dream.

06:35.362 --> 06:36.728
It's sort of gloomy.

06:36.730 --> 06:38.330
Is that 'cause I'm,
I don't know,

06:38.332 --> 06:39.664
mad at my family?

06:39.666 --> 06:41.066
Is that how fever dreams work?

06:41.068 --> 06:42.734
                 Hey, I say just
               have fun with it.

06:42.736 --> 06:44.836
Jeez.
I got to tell you, Kuch,

06:44.838 --> 06:46.171
it's kind of hard
to look at you.

06:46.173 --> 06:48.173
           Is it bad?
           It's bad.

06:48.175 --> 06:49.875
Not in the face, though, right?

