                       Too much?
         Hey, I just remembered.

06:56.350 --> 06:58.850
            I have a place here.
                   A time share.

06:58.852 --> 07:00.919
You have a time share
in my fever dream?

07:00.921 --> 07:03.355
 Yes, it's a beautiful fortress.
                          There!

07:03.357 --> 07:05.257
You can just see it.
                       Oh, yeah.

07:05.259 --> 07:07.025
                 Are you looking
             where I'm pointing?

07:07.027 --> 07:09.194
Yeah, it's, like,
the only fortress.

07:09.196 --> 07:11.563
               Right, but you're
              not reacting like,

07:11.565 --> 07:13.765
                "Whoa, that's an
           incredible fortress."

07:13.767 --> 07:15.534
It's very nice,
it's very nice.

07:15.536 --> 07:17.235
                       Anyway...

07:17.237 --> 07:18.570
  we should totally go there.

