    We can be alone, and...

07:20.073 --> 07:21.740
          (whispers):
      we'll be safe there.

07:21.742 --> 07:22.741
        Safe from what?

07:22.743 --> 07:24.042
             Safe from everyone.

07:24.044 --> 07:25.210
            No one will hurt us!

07:25.212 --> 07:26.545
Whoa.
                   Sorry.

07:26.547 --> 07:29.047
Yeah.
                 Okay, well, um,

07:29.049 --> 07:30.715
          yeah, let's get going.

07:30.717 --> 07:32.050
Sounds good.

07:32.052 --> 07:33.385
             LINDA:
       <i> Oh, this is awful!</i>

