09:28.669 --> 09:29.701
Well, ho-hold on.

09:29.703 --> 09:31.236
Look, Bakeneko,

09:31.238 --> 09:32.837
    you don't tell me where
       I can and can't go

09:32.839 --> 09:34.372
     in my own fever dream.

09:34.374 --> 09:35.707
       Why do you want to
        go there anyway?

09:35.709 --> 09:37.842
Well if you must know,
to be alone.

09:37.844 --> 09:39.544
       Pfft. That's dumb.
          You're dumb.

09:39.546 --> 09:41.212
     Your face is... dumb.

09:41.214 --> 09:42.881
(quietly):
My face is not dumb.

09:42.883 --> 09:44.716
Beat the bear.
        Bup bup bup bup bup bup.

09:44.718 --> 09:46.351
       (chuckles) I really don't
              want to fight you.

09:46.353 --> 09:48.687
     Ah, then let us pass.
           Okay, I'll fight you.

09:48.689 --> 09:51.056
         But I'll go easy on you
       because I'm so big and...

09:51.058 --> 09:53.725
        (Lousie grunts,
 Bakeneko groans, then wheezes)
         Okay, not bad.

09:53.727 --> 09:55.193
       All... you have...
                      (grunting)

09:55.195 --> 09:57.562
  to do... is let... us pass!

09:57.564 --> 10:00.565
    (high-pitched grunting):
I'm not... trying... my hardest.

